Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.57,0:01:48.70,*Default1,46,0000,0000,0000,,夕立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.13,0:01:57.23,*Default5,47,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.23,0:02:02.03,*Default5,48,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不要緊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.03,0:02:03.13,*Default5,49,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.03,0:02:05.23,*Default5,50,0000,0000,0000,,臉色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.23,0:02:06.63,*Default5,51,0000,0000,0000,,不太好唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.53,*Default5,52,0000,0000,0000,,之前的休假有好好休息嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.03,0:02:12.13,*Default5,53,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.53,0:02:15.13,*Default5,54,0000,0000,0000,,感覺上還老是在發呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.13,0:02:17.13,*Default5,55,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.13,0:02:20.43,*Default5,56,0000,0000,0000,,辦活動的時候可要打起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.43,0:02:22.23,*Default5,57,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.63,0:02:26.23,*Default5,58,0000,0000,0000,,還念念不忘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.83,0:02:28.93,*Default5,59,0000,0000,0000,,失戀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.33,0:02:32.13,*Default5,60,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.73,0:02:34.53,*Default5,61,0000,0000,0000,,那不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.83,0:02:43.03,*Default5,62,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}事實上{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.63,0:02:51.73,*Default5,63,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}關於被甩這件事, 我已經沒有任何依戀與執著{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.43,0:03:01.73,*Default5,64,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}耕四郎你...有從心裡真正喜歡過誰嗎?{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.73,0:03:06.73,*Default5,65,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}沒有{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.23,0:03:09.23,*Default5,66,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我抓不到訣竅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.33,*Default5,67,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}看不出來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.33,*Default5,68,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}然後我跌倒了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.03,0:03:13.83,*Default5,69,0000,0000,0000,,小田切!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.83,0:03:14.83,*Default5,70,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.43,0:03:18.03,*Default5,71,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}但是我平常很冷靜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.93,0:03:33.43,*Default5,72,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?今晚的慶功宴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.23,*Default5,73,0000,0000,0000,,是所長要請客唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.23,0:03:37.03,*Default5,74,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 太好了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.73,*Default5,75,0000,0000,0000,,當然要去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.03,*Default5,76,0000,0000,0000,,我另外有約, 要先回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.73,*Default5,77,0000,0000,0000,,有約?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.73,0:03:45.73,*Default5,78,0000,0000,0000,,看電影啦! 電影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.73,*Default5,79,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是跟七夏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.53,*Default5,80,0000,0000,0000,,就算是那樣又怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.53,0:03:55.63,*Default5,81,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒辦法呀, 是她約我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.43,*Default5,82,0000,0000,0000,,請帶我一起去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.43,0:03:59.33,*Default5,83,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦! 你要跟所長一起去喝酒吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.93,*Default5,84,0000,0000,0000,,耕四郎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.63,0:04:09.53,*Default5,85,0000,0000,0000,,上次...我們來這裡開會的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.53,0:04:13.43,*Default5,86,0000,0000,0000,,你跟一個女高中生搭訕對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.53,*Default5,87,0000,0000,0000,,搭訕!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.73,*Default5,88,0000,0000,0000,,跟女高中生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.03,0:04:21.33,*Default5,89,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.33,0:04:22.53,*Default5,90,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.83,*Default5,91,0000,0000,0000,,果然是七夏對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.73,*Default5,92,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就說是你妹妹不就好了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.93,*Default5,93,0000,0000,0000,,小田切. 幫我搬這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.13,*Default5,94,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.93,0:05:03.23,*Default5,95,0000,0000,0000,,跟七夏搭訕是怎麼一回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.83,*Default5,96,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.83,*Default5,97,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.83,*Default5,98,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.13,0:05:27.03,*Default5,99,0000,0000,0000,,不要一付那麼稀奇的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.63,*Default5,100,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.13,0:05:31.13,*Default5,101,0000,0000,0000,,早上的時候明明還有鬍子的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.13,0:05:34.63,*Default5,102,0000,0000,0000,,因為辦活動時要是不剃乾淨會被罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.43,*Default5,103,0000,0000,0000,,剃乾淨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.43,*Default5,104,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.13,*Default5,105,0000,0000,0000,,很帥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.83,*Default5,106,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像很痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.03,*Default5,107,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.33,*Default5,108,0000,0000,0000,,這部電影啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.93,*Default5,109,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠那麼近!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.43,0:06:19.83,*Default5,110,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.83,0:06:20.93,*Default5,111,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.03,*Default5,112,0000,0000,0000,,妳在發什麼呆?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.73,0:06:29.83,*Default5,113,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.13,0:06:34.43,*Default5,114,0000,0000,0000,,學生證拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.53,*Default5,115,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.43,*Default5,116,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.63,0:07:05.03,*Default5,117,0000,0000,0000,,我去買票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.23,0:07:30.93,*Default5,118,0000,0000,0000,,這種時間讓妳自己一個人回來, 他在想什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.93,*Default5,119,0000,0000,0000,,他叫我先回來就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.83,0:07:36.63,*Default5,120,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿他沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.03,0:07:40.43,*Default5,121,0000,0000,0000,,電影一結束就匆匆忙忙跑到別的地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.53,*Default5,122,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙去哪了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.53,0:07:46.93,*Default5,123,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道, 他什麼也沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.13,*Default5,124,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.63,*Default5,125,0000,0000,0000,,制服會皺掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.13,*Default5,126,0000,0000,0000,,才不管那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.23,0:08:03.93,*Default5,127,0000,0000,0000,,有事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.13,*Default5,128,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.13,*Default5,129,0000,0000,0000,,那個是我妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.43,*Default5,130,0000,0000,0000,,也許我沒跟妳說過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.43,0:08:23.13,*Default5,131,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹之前一直住別的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.03,0:08:27.83,*Default5,132,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道我父母離婚對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.83,0:08:30.93,*Default5,133,0000,0000,0000,,然後她一直跟著我媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.93,0:08:34.43,*Default5,134,0000,0000,0000,,這個春天開始, 因為這裡離學校比較近\N所以就住在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.03,*Default5,135,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.93,0:08:47.33,*Default5,136,0000,0000,0000,,真的就這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.93,0:08:49.93,*Default5,137,0000,0000,0000,,啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.43,*Default5,138,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.83,*Default5,139,0000,0000,0000,,你說有話要說, 我還以為是什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.53,*Default5,140,0000,0000,0000,,這又不是什麼好笑的事!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.53,0:09:08.93,*Default5,141,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想被妳想成是\N剛分手就對女高中生下手的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.93,*Default5,142,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還期待了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.33,0:09:18.93,*Default5,143,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會在意女高中生什麼的\N是挺像耕四郎你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.33,*Default5,144,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.33,*Default5,145,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再為這種事來找妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.63,0:09:35.83,*Default5,146,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.53,*Default5,147,0000,0000,0000,,吃過了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.93,0:09:50.83,*Default5,148,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}突然, 腦子裡閃過了一個無聊的念頭{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.23,0:09:58.03,*Default5,149,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}想起來, 距上次做愛已經三個月了...{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.78,*Default5,150,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}可以了吧? 妳又不會喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.28,*Default5,151,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}才沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.28,0:10:55.38,*Default5,152,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}就是這樣! 我比你厲害多了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.78,*Default5,153,0000,0000,0000,,好吃對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.08,*Default5,154,0000,0000,0000,,很少人知道這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.18,*Default5,155,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.88,*Default5,156,0000,0000,0000,,我常常一個人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.18,0:11:22.18,*Default5,157,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你說什麼啊? 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.08,*Default5,158,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}什麼笨蛋? 我是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.08,*Default5,159,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我才不信!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.98,*Default5,160,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這種事情可不是開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.58,*Default5,161,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}祥子呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.88,0:11:33.78,*Default5,162,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}她只是普通朋友..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.78,0:11:34.98,*Default5,163,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}騙人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.98,0:11:36.98,*Default5,164,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真的真的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.58,0:11:38.78,*Default5,165,0000,0000,0000,,妳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.98,*Default5,166,0000,0000,0000,,最近工作怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.18,*Default5,167,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這樣問?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.68,*Default5,168,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是一直說要辭掉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.88,*Default5,169,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.88,0:11:50.68,*Default5,170,0000,0000,0000,,聽妳抱怨那麼多次, 怎麼可能忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.58,0:11:58.08,*Default5,171,0000,0000,0000,,每次都只是隨便應對\N我還以為你都沒在聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.88,*Default5,172,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.78,*Default5,173,0000,0000,0000,,那麼, 工作到底怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.98,0:12:05.98,*Default5,174,0000,0000,0000,,普通...吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.78,*Default5,175,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.98,0:12:09.98,*Default5,176,0000,0000,0000,,你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.28,0:12:11.78,*Default5,177,0000,0000,0000,,今天有活動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.78,0:12:12.88,*Default5,178,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.78,0:12:18.08,*Default5,179,0000,0000,0000,,還是...因為女高中生的關係而刮了鬍子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.68,*Default5,180,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.28,*Default5,181,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.28,*Default5,182,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.38,*Default5,183,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.98,0:13:46.38,*Default5,184,0000,0000,0000,,沒有, 只是想說計程車怎麼都沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.68,0:13:50.38,*Default5,185,0000,0000,0000,,往前走就會通到大馬路\N那邊計程車會比較好叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.18,0:13:57.68,*Default5,186,0000,0000,0000,,下個月我要搬家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.08,0:14:01.68,*Default5,187,0000,0000,0000,,工作也會辭掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.18,*Default5,188,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.08,0:14:05.18,*Default5,189,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.08,0:14:10.58,*Default5,190,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提, 等下我男朋友要來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.88,0:14:12.88,*Default5,191,0000,0000,0000,,喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.38,*Default5,192,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.28,*Default5,193,0000,0000,0000,,他是個很棒的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.18,*Default5,194,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
