Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.58,0:14:28.88,*Default5,196,0000,0000,0000,,真的要加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.18,*Default5,197,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
