Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.58,0:14:48.58,*Default5,200,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}真的是太好了{\i0}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.88,*Default5,201,0000,0000,0000,,別待到太晚喔!
